1. *Viđenja* nam je bilo kratko, ali smo se uspeli zabaviti. (The meeting was short, but we managed to have fun.)
2. *Viđenju* smo se oboje radovali. (We both looked forward to the meeting.)
3. On se nada da će se uskoro imati priliku za *viđenje*. (He hopes to have an opportunity to meet soon.)
4. *Viđenja* uživamo svakog dana. (We enjoy meeting each other every day.)
5. Oni su se dugo čekali na *viđenje*. (They waited a long time to meet each other.)